{
  "info": {
    "name": "Studify - Institute (Government) User Journey",
    "description": "Complete Postman collection for Institute/Government user flows.\n\nCovers: Auth - Profile - Categories - Products - Cart - Checkout - Orders - Transactions\n\nSeeded Test Users:\n- Phone: +209000000001 (Ministry of Health)\n- Phone: +209000000002 (Ministry of Education)\n- Phone: +209000000003 (Ministry of Interior)\n- Phone: +209000000004 (Financial Oversight)\n- Phone: +209000000005 (Ministry of Electricity)\n- Password for all: Password123!\n\nHow to use:\n1. Run **LOGIN (Seeded Institute)** — token is saved automatically via collection Bearer auth.\n2. Run **Get All Institute Products** (or list with `categoryId`) — saves `product_id` from the first institute product.\n3. **Add Product to Cart** then **Create Wholesale Order** (checkout is wholesale, not regular orders).\n\nCategories & products (government catalogue):\n- Four main categories (no ` / ` in name): تجهيز المواد الاوليه، القرطاسية، مستلزمات عامة، الاثاث المكتبي.\n- Sub-categories in API/DB: `MainName / SubName` (space-slash-space). `GET /products?categoryId=<main_or_sub_id>` returns only products in that branch (main = all subs under it).\n- Retail (`isInstituteCategory: false`) and institute (`true`) stay separated by user type and flags — same JSON shape as before: `{ success, message, data, pagination? }`.\n\nTroubleshooting:\n- **Cart: wholesale / institute product required**: You are INSTITUTE but `referenceId` points to a **retail** product. Call catalogue **with Bearer token** (`/api/products` or `/api/mobile/products`), or use **Get All Institute Products** so `product_id` is wholesale.\n- **JWT must be INSTITUTE**: Login with `\"clientType\": \"INSTITUTE\"` for a phone registered as INSTITUTE.\n- **No customer profile / wholesale**: Institute checkout needs a **Customer** row (seed + new register include it).\n- **Mixed cart**: **Clear Entire Cart** then add again.\n- **Seed**: `npm run prisma:seed:institute` from backend (re-run safe; products dedupe by name).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "host", "value": "localhost", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "port", "value": "6008", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refresh_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "user_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "customer_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "product_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "category_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "cart_item_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "order_id", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01 - Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register New Institute User",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["var json = pm.response.json();", "if(json.data && json.data.user) pm.collectionVariables.set('user_id', json.data.user.id);", "if(json.data && json.data.userId) pm.collectionVariables.set('user_id', json.data.userId);"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"+964770001234\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\",\n  \"type\": \"INSTITUTE\",\n  \"email\": \"new-institute@gov.iq\",\n  \"name\": \"New Government Institute\"\n}" },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:6008/api/auth/register",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "6008",
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify OTP",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["var json = pm.response.json();", "if(json.data && json.data.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);", "if(json.data && json.data.refreshToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', json.data.refreshToken);"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"{{user_id}}\",\n  \"code\": \"123456\"\n}" },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:6008/api/auth/verify-otp",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "6008",
              "path": ["api", "auth", "verify-otp"]
            },
            "description": "Enter the 6-digit OTP. For dev, check console or DB."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Resend OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"{{user_id}}\"\n}" },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:6008/api/auth/resend-otp",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "6008",
              "path": ["api", "auth", "resend-otp"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "LOGIN (Seeded Institute - Health Ministry)",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["var json = pm.response.json();", "if(json.data){", "  if(json.data.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);", "  if(json.data.refreshToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', json.data.refreshToken);", "  if(json.data.user){", "    pm.collectionVariables.set('user_id', json.data.user.id);", "    if(json.data.user.customer) pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_id', json.data.user.customer.id);", "  }", "}", "pm.test('Login returns 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });", "pm.test('Logged-in user type is INSTITUTE', function () { pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true; pm.expect(json.data && json.data.user && json.data.user.type).to.eql('INSTITUTE'); });", "pm.test('Bearer token saved to collection', function () { pm.expect(pm.collectionVariables.get('token')).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty; });"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"+209000000001\",\n  \"password\": \"Password123!\",\n  \"clientType\": \"INSTITUTE\"\n}" },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:6008/api/auth/login",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "6008",
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login with seeded institute user. Token auto-saved to variable."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get My Profile",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["var json = pm.response.json();", "if(json.data && json.data.customer) pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_id', json.data.customer.id);"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:6008/api/auth/profile",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "6008",
              "path": ["api", "auth", "profile"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Change Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"currentPassword\": \"Password123!\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"NewSecure456!\"\n}" },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:6008/api/mobile/customer/change-password",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "6008",
              "path": ["api", "mobile", "customer", "change-password"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
